title: [Guardian Keep, Grassy Sward]
description: Long colorful banners wave from the poles of the different kiosks and tents that are set up throughout the area of this grassy sward.  A few scattered groups of elven children can be seen playing tag and other games in the open spaces that exist between the various shops.

Long dark banners wave from the poles of the different kiosks and tents that are set up throughout the area of this grassy sward.  The occasional person walks through the area, shadowed by the night's darkness on errands of an unknown nature.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, south, west
